Well, I made it to NG++. IIRC, the First Warden on NG+ hit me for like 8 damage in full heavy armor. On NG++ he hit me for 12. I played a bit further and noticed a very sharp increase in damage from certain monsters in the first area of the game; so yeah, the difficulty technically increases.

The shame is that it took so long to get this way. The gameworld is quite small once you run through it once and that newness" feeling wears off. Its cramped
